---
name: translate_to_spanish
description: Translate English text into Spanish.
model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: openai
    base_url: ${env:OPENAI_BASE_URL}
    api_key: ${env:OPENAI_API_KEY}
    name: gpt-4
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.3
inputs:
  text_input:
    type: string
sample:
  text_input: "Hello, world!"
---

system:
You are a translator.

user:
Translate the following English text into Spanish:

{{text_input}}
